ong architectural feature within a high-traffic public environment. The proposal reimagines the staircase as both a functional connector and a visual anchor within the larger interior.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">The rendered design focuses on clean geometry, material cohesion, and clear sightlines to support spatial flow. Refined detailing, integrated handrails, and a restrained material palette were envisioned to elevate the experience of movement while responding to the scale of the surrounding area.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Through detailed visualization and design studies, the concept demonstrates how a thoughtfully designed staircase can contribute to the identity and clarity of a public space, turning circulation into a purposeful design moment. </p></div><div class="z-10 relative right-0 left-0 h-12 pt-10"><div class="z-10 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 bottom-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white from-70% to-transparent transition-opacity duration-300 opacity-100"></div><button type="button" aria-label="Read More" class="relative z-20 hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity pt-4"><p class="text-current font-body text-md font-bold">Read More</p></button></div></div></div></div><div class="col-start-1 md:col-start-3 md:col-end-11 col-end-13 lg:col-start-7 lg:col-end-12 xl:col-end-11"><div role="button" class="cursor-zoom-in hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity"><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F9f85dc8f82d5f0a40578dced1f1565c7a0ec7641-2600x1450.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F9f85dc8f82d5f0a40578dced1f1565c7a0ec7641-2600x1450.png&w=3840&q=75amp;q=75 1x" alt="" width="2600" height="1450" class="w-full h-full" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 50vw, 33vw"/></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pb-unit md:pb-24